Main
Class getUserValue

java.lang.Object
  Main.getUserValue

public class getUserValue
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to obtain stats about a user. Given the user's name and the location of the server database, a string with the specific stat will be returned.

Author:
Nicholas Ingalls
